   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the left panel under Group, select <uicontrol>Email Recipients</uicontrol>. </p>
            <stepresult>The Active Email Recipients page is displayed.</stepresult>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To create a new Email Recipients record, click <uicontrol>New</uicontrol> from the
               ribbon at the top of the page. </p>
            <stepresult>The New Email Recipients page is displayed.</stepresult>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the full <uicontrol>Name, First Name, </uicontrol>and <uicontrol>Last Name </uicontrol>of the email recipient.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the <uicontrol>Email Id </uicontrol>of the recipient.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>From Send Email, select one of the following:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>To send an email notification to the recipient, select <uicontrol>Yes</uicontrol>.</li>
                  <li>To disable email notification for a recipient, select <uicontrol>No</uicontrol>.</li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Save &amp; Close</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
